         <abstract id="aspace_559b1c69e3ebadfa2c1da065ad61b201">The papers consist of personal papers, memorabilia, photographs and medals of James Dowling Trask (1890-1942), his father and grandfather (1821-1883), also named James Dowling Trask.  The bulk of the collection is related to James Dowling Trask (1890-1942).</abstract>
